# VISION

Build a platform where developers can collaborate
on structured knowledge with AI.

Success criteria:
- 100 active users in 3 months
- Sub-second render times

# CONTEXT

Target users: developers and architects.

Constraints:
- Must work offline
- Must support Git versioning

| Environment | Status |
| --- | --- |
| Node 18+ | Required |
| Browser | Supported |

# STRUCTURE

## System Architecture

The system consists of three main components:

### Parser Engine

Reads `.kdoc` files and produces the document model.

### Render Engine

Multiple output formats from a single source.

### AI Assistant

Generates plans and tasks from vision.

## Data Model

```
Document
  ├ metadata
  ├ sections[]
  └ assets[]
```

# PLAN

## Phase 1 — Prototype

- Parser implementation
- Basic HTML renderer

## Phase 2 — Editor

- VS Code extension
- Syntax highlighting

## Phase 3 — AI

- Plan generation
- Task generation

